# Panchang Paheli (Calendar Puzzle)

<catsoop-section>Introduction</catsoop-section>

Imagine your calendar turning into a playground, where each day brings a new challenge to uncover the date! Prepare to stretch your brain, conquer each day's puzzle, and uncover the hidden magic within these pieces. Let the polyomino adventure begin!

<catsoop-section>Materials Required</catsoop-section>

- Pentomino Puzzle Pieces
- Calendar Grid

